name: Dekni x Madzilla x Lost Kats iPhone4
description:
Madelyn Lance, aka "Madzilla," has been heating up instagram and web feeds for quite some time now, amassing loyal followers with her signature looks. When Dekni teamed up with Lost Kats owner Bobby Brackins to collaborate on a new and exclusive phone case, it was a no brainer to pay tribute to the modern icon whose style and lifestyle both equally captivate thousands. Combining the talented photography of Lost Kats with Dekni's precision engraving technique's yielded a product that's as much as a statement as it is a benchmark. As Madzilla's tattoos tell the story of her past, let our collaborative phone case embolden your present, and protect your presence.

-Hand Waxed
-Laser Engraved
-Two Piece Protective Case

FREE SHIPPING in the United States.

name: Sacred Geometry iPhone 4
description:
It's no secret that Scared Geometry is one of the common loves binding Dekni Creations to the M.E.C.C.A. Collective. So when Dekni founder Chad Markey reached out to M.E.C.C.A. leader David Baker for ideas on new phone case designs, its only fitting that Baker answered with his take on the Dekni insignia by beautifully incorporating triangles of all shapes and sizes into our logo. Conceptually simple but complex in execution, Baker's Sacred Geometry Design is a testament to our shared interests, styles and bonds with the M.E.C.C.A Collective.
